knowledgeGraph.title: Donald Trump
knowledgeGraph.description: Donald John Trump is an American politician, media personality, and businessman who is the 47th president of the United States. A member of the Republican Party, he served as the 45th president from 2017 to 2021.

attributes.Children: Barron Trump, Ivanka Trump, Tiffany Trump, and more
